{
  "stem": "4662.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he did come back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When was that?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Didn't he say a date?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was-- it was something before my mother-in-law's birthday--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "28Th of April, she's-- her birthday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I think it was just around near there that he came back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't say with certainty which dates it were anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was at-- I think I was at my mother-in-laws.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where was I when he came home?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was at home, in my-- in the little flat, where I always was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came back there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We told him I was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think that's the way it went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was just fat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had a head swollen up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was so fat all over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They'd-- he'd only had turnips to eat, and then they get swelled up from turnips.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He looked awful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I couldn't-- I didn't know him, even, he was so changed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they was-- they, they really didn't know what was happening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My eldest son may have known more than my youngest son.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I kept that as much as I could from them because we had to lead a normal life.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if they knew anything, they would be liable to talk to somebody, or let something loose.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, the Gestapo used to live around the corner.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one day, I went into the bedroom, my children made all little paper balls like this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were lighting them up with matches, leaning over the window, waiting for the Gestapo to go by so that they could-- so they could throw the fireballs at them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just caught them in time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Terrifying.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think I just told them, he's away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He'll be back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's away.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They really didn't understand, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
